---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner container-wide">
    <!-- Top row -->
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="footer-wordmark">
          <span class="wk">간병연구소</span>
          <span class="we">CaregiverLab</span>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-tagline">간병의 기준을 만듭니다.</p>
        <p class="footer-desc">
          간병 현장의 데이터와 제도 정보를 연구·정리합니다.<br />
          출처와 집계 방법을 명시한 브리프·가이드를 제공합니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="footer-nav" aria-label="푸터 내비게이션">
        <div class="footer-nav-group">
          <div class="footer-nav-label">콘텐츠</div>
          <a href="/research/">리서치</a>
          <a href="/insights/">Insights</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-nav-group">
          <div class="footer-nav-label">연구소</div>
          <a href="/about/">About</a>
          <a href="/contact/">문의</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="footer-rule"></div>

    <!-- Bottom row -->
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="footer-copy">
        © {year} 간병연구소. 모든 문서의 무단 전재·재배포를 금합니다.
      </p>
      <p class="footer-disclaimer">
        본 사이트의 정보는 참고용이며, 법적·의료적 판단의 근거로 사용할 수 없습니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
.site-footer {
  background: var(--ink);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin-top: auto;
}
.footer-inner { padding: 56px 24px 32px; }
.footer-top {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 40px;
  align-items: start;
}
.footer-wordmark {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.wk {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 17px;
  color: #fff;
}
.we {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}
.footer-tagline {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.footer-desc {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}
.footer-nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 40px;
}
.footer-nav-group {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
  min-width: 100px;
}
.footer-nav-label {
  font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.footer-nav-group a {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.14s;
}
.footer-nav-group a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
.footer-rule {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  margin: 40px 0 20px;
}
.footer-bottom {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.footer-copy, .footer-disclaimer {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  .footer-nav { flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
}
</style>
